  "text": "where T m is the melting temperature of the nanosolid, T mb is the bulk melting temperature corresponding to the material of the nanosolid, D is the crystal size of the nanosolid, and C is a material constant. Qi [CITATION_1] further developed Equation (13) as seen in Equation (14):",
